data.text:
Looking to travel from Frinton-on-Sea to Brentwood by train? You've come to the right place!

On average, it takes around 3 hours 8 minutes to travel from Frinton-on-Sea to Brentwood by train, the fastest services can get you there in as little as 1 hour 14 minutes though. You'll usually find 24 trains per day running along the 43 miles (70 km) route between these two destinations. You'll need to make 1 change during the journey to Brentwood, as there currently aren't any direct services on this route. Greater Anglia are the main train operator on this route and will whisk you to Brentwood in no time.

To help you get great train deals, we'll highlight the cheapest train ticket prices from Frinton-on-Sea to Brentwood in our Journey Planner. Just remember, as well as travelling Off-Peak or using a Railcard, the sooner you book your tickets, the more you'll save!

Want to book your train tickets now? Just start a search with us today. If you want to find out more about the journey, scroll up for timetables including live train times, or keep reading for FAQs and tips on how to book cheap train tickets.
